Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}『WOLF字幕組』      (www.wolfsub.com)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若狹海浪逐沙灘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀉湖佛體破不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,襤褸衣中魂依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傲首憑風笛聲顫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說變就變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 聊點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊？聊什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剛才那事 赤帝軍的「圍剿」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的全都說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是親眼看見的 具體情況我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說過吸血鬼的事沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼？德古拉伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}愛爾蘭作家布萊姆·斯托克寫的《德古拉》一書中作為主人公登場的吸血鬼德古拉伯爵Dracula
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說這帶也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是「浩劫」的影響？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙有尖銳的牙齒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見漂亮的女人就會像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嗚一口！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想繼續就再拿錢來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到什麼線索沒？萊依
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 全都是些道聽途說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可笑 什麼吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你還是別這麼幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老老實實地收集情報可不合我的脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到能幫上忙的傢伙沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磨破了鐵鞋結果被野狗盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 這次打賭我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下啊 還沒到說好的時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼想和我睡麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攬客
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九點酒船見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是這麼說 其實八字還沒一撇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥 來耍耍不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼國？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦子有病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛鳥？大和的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}九郎誤以為日本大和時代的皇都飛鳥 因其發音與明日香相同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還帶這麼危險的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從哪兒來的？在找人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中招了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剛才那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧 找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爺 問個事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌留多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們今天這裏在這兒做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在割蘆場那 今天跟明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管帳的是雪組？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 風組
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 謝謝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 歌留多先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉 今天也很靚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼 歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值不了幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混賬！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停 停 停！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌留多先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這刀我買了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是哪跟哪的嘛 您要就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的話就跟我來 去家叫酒船的店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎 你哪兒來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了酒還是悶聲不吭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敦巴的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有個上司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘是畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這畫畫的是「浩劫」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「浩劫」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是隕石撞了地球七天七夜那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了從頭說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情發生在二十四年前 一顆小行星接近地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了摧毀小行星世界各國都發射了核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜沒來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著混亂 某些國家按下了將核彈射向他國的按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是國家之間相繼進行還擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果 那些強國全都毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就算這樣 世界上應該起碼還有七成的人能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是接下來發生的事足以毀滅全世界的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 是所有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是「冬夜」時代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「冬夜」持續了一年多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到露出陽光 白天漸漸恢復的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是兩年半之後的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這段時期裏 據說日本的人口降到了百分之一以下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候電視和廣播都不管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界上到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人能全部知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說呢？九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼來這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來「圍剿」已經全面展開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒船裏有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊依！萊依！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上把燈都關了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後進畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲畫裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝軍來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌留多  聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在赤帝軍的直升機往你們那飛過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵軍有多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來偵察的有6個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離酒船入口還有15米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30秒內就會進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 你也進去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你力氣真是嚇人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這傷口能癒合的話 那就讓我們後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要幹什麼

